admin().details: Returns the address of the current admin.

getLevelUpFee(uint256).details: The address of the ClockAuction contract that handles sales of Kitties.  This same contract handles both peer-to-peer.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

setLevelUpFee(uint256,uint256,uint256).details: Updates the level up fee as well as mint fee. Can only  be called by the Admin address. todo: maxLevel todo: maxLevel todo

transferAdmin(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newAdmin`). Can only be called by the current admin.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

maxLevelOfOwner.details: A mapping from Voyager to the max level of the Voyager.

tokenLevelCount.details: A mapping from owner to token amount of each level.

voyagers.details: An array containing the Voyager struct for all Voyagers in existence. The ID of each Voyager is actually an index into this array.
